        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7395",
        "content": "Among which, he set down first what satisfaction should be given by any one who should steal anything belonging to the Church, the bishop, or the other clergy, for he was resolved to give protection to those whom he had received along with their doctrine.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
