        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7395",
        "content": "The bishop, being carried thither by his servants, weak as he was, set about averting by prayer the danger which the strong hands of active men had not been able to overcome with all their exertions.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
