        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7395",
        "content": "How Honorius, who succeeded Justus in the bishopric of Canterbury, received the pall and letters from Pope Honorius. [six thirty four a d]",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
